  "text": "The notations are classical and identical to those of [CITATION_1] , where all terms are more formally detailed. This system is positive if and only if the matrices A, B, C, D, L, G have only positive entries [CITATION_2] . Note also that in this paper we only require the positivity of the filter to be designed and not of the system Σ, but it can be assumed because otherwise it is not necessary to design a positive filter.",
